snippet.title: GTA Alien City - Halloween Special 2020
snippet.description:
What year is it? What planet is this? Let me check myself, am I dead? CJ is on a mission like a super technician in Grand Theft Auto: Alien City! This is a full conversion mod for San Andreas with a brand new map, storyline, characters, and more! The Truth is out there! 👽
